{"tid":1742384,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【十萬火急】唔好再俾陳彥霖同學嘅事悲劇重演！！！","createTime":"2019-11-20T18:42:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T11:16:55.000Z","uid":332999,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5884a57528e059c26f3888fad20f2bd40def939b","tid":1742384,"uid":332999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T18:42:09.000Z","msg":"將軍澳17歲少女裸跳單野，用個屎忽諗都知有古怪，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果班黑警身有屎，一定會諗盡辦法，拿拿林搞個火葬張單案close file一天光哂！</span></span></span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以求下大家唔好俾單野沉水！！小心又九秒九落葬！！唔好又俾黑警得逞！！一定要還番女學生一個公道！！一定追住份驗屍報道唔放！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">同埋如果有人識女學生嘅家屬嘅話，一定要叫佢哋小心d！！！唔知都要搜出黎！！</span></span></strong>因為黑警一定會叫佢哋認完屍即搞葬禮，到時有咩傾唔埋就唔知又會唔會被消失。唔好又再俾黑警捷足先登！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳同學嘅事係我哋唔夠防範，今次已經唔係第一次，唔好又走返陳同學嘅路！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">極極極急唔知點解無人講！！！求推</span></span></span></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9703708197b36b39253b503bdbec6dfe12d8156","tid":1742384,"uid":110570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T18:42:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ca7e708ff8776224d4037fd2e79327074926c7b0","tid":1742384,"uid":95499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T18:43:45.000Z","msg":"其實都擺到明係黑警殺 但係我地仲可以點"},{"pid":"f886821746295b9d2157fea74abd03f8b88bda3d","tid":1742384,"uid":332999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca7e708ff8776224d4037fd2e79327074926c7b0","tid":1742384,"uid":95499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T18:43:45.000Z","msg":"其實都擺到明係黑警殺 但係我地仲可以點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T18:52:02.000Z","msg":"真係可以做嘅野有限<br />\n只能夠繼續煲大佢<br />\n點都唔可以對黑警d暴行麻木哂"},{"pid":"1f75738d9d150422144fac407aa3f4803f611080","tid":1742384,"uid":332999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T18:55:07.000Z","msg":"其實老實講而加係無證據吹佢哋唔漲<br />\n總會有一日有街坊影住佢哋拋屍"},{"pid":"c24b6ae815a86d7dcb89813447328f6f60e08158","tid":1742384,"uid":20428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T22:29:49.000Z","msg":"偵探又黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />區選啦"},{"pid":"41d8ae86ad4a2860b95738e836092d9a5665af4b","tid":1742384,"uid":286499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T22:33:42.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8151eede38f0a6c98b7ebbeefc916d7f66633ee3","tid":1742384,"uid":16458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T22:52:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"876599de2192a3eacd2abd08c19ab2d1303efc9a","tid":1742384,"uid":265917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T22:53:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3aa42c13777fe3f0cb21cab86c27720ae7a0c64","tid":1742384,"uid":173011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T22:54:13.000Z","msg":"我更加相信係共產黨殺，犬係幫兇去隱瞞事實"},{"pid":"b5f38aad16ba4ea40e7e346df2713519fdc53922","tid":1742384,"uid":278349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T23:02:14.000Z","msg":"幾時先死一隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e597164000d876e6e00d8f73afaa1ad64175acc","tid":1742384,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T11:16:55.000Z","